<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Incredible. The Evo III is pinned
down and can't get ahead.</b></font>

301
00:34:20,154 --> 00:34:25,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Damn, I can't take advantage of the
misfiring system or the 4WD's traction.</b></font>

302
00:34:35,964 --> 00:34:36,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He did it!</b></font>

303
00:34:36,964 --> 00:34:38,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He reversed it!</b></font>

304
00:34:43,754 --> 00:34:45,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He did it!</b></font>

305
00:34:48,864 --> 00:34:55,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66" color="#ffff00"><b>{\an5}Unable to overcome the new</b></font>

306
00:34:48,864 --> 00:34:55,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66" color="#ffff00"><b>{\an5}engine, Takumi finds Saitama's</b></font>

307
00:34:48,864 --> 00:34:55,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66" color="#ffff00"><b>{\an5}fastest, Wataru Akiyama, before him.</b></font>

308
00:34:48,864 --> 00:34:55,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66" color="#ffff00"><b>{\an5}Even with his race-prepped engine,</b></font>

309
00:34:48,864 --> 00:34:55,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66" color="#ffff00"><b>{\an5}Takumi feels distant, spurring Wataru</b></font>

310
00:34:48,864 --> 00:34:55,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66" color="#ffff00"><b>{\an5}to challenge him.</b></font>

311
00:35:05,774 --> 00:35:08,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let me observe you
thoroughly from behind...</b></font>

312
00:35:08,334 --> 00:35:11,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...and see your true potential, which has
never been defeated in the Gunma area.</b></font>

313
00:35:15,434 --> 00:35:18,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's so difficult to drive here.
What's with this place?</b></font>

314
00:35:36,984 --> 00:35:38,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What was that?</b></font>

315
00:35:38,884 --> 00:35:40,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Was it just my imagination?</b></font>

316
00:35:41,014 --> 00:35:43,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It was so hard until yesterday.</b></font>

317
00:35:44,894 --> 00:35:48,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can control it and
drive it as I like.</b></font>

318
00:35:53,304 --> 00:35:55,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's not the speed of a first timer.</b></font>

319
00:35:56,894 --> 00:35:58,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm so thrilled.</b></font>

320
00:35:58,594 --> 00:36:00,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There're many incredible
guys outside my area.</b></font>

321
00:36:27,824 --> 00:36:30,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six is
finally accepting me.</b></font>

322
00:36:31,094 --> 00:36:34,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I want to win. I've never felt
such a strong desire to win.</b></font>

323
00:36:35,384 --> 00:36:38,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway, I want to
win with this car.</b></font>

324
00:36:39,584 --> 00:36:44,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As the conditions worsen,
he looks more skilled.</b></font>

325
00:36:44,774 --> 00:36:49,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But he's human. The first to lose
his concentration will be the loser.</b></font>

326
00:36:49,924 --> 00:36:51,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is a match of how
long one can endure.</b></font>

327
00:37:17,124 --> 00:37:22,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's getting really tough,
but he must feel the same.</b></font>

328
00:37:22,894 --> 00:37:27,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even if there's a slight difference in our pace,
you can't overtake me on this course.</b></font>

329
00:37:27,694 --> 00:37:30,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When you lose, it's always the chaser
who's been outrun by the leader.</b></font>

330
00:37:36,994 --> 00:37:38,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What the...?</b></font>

331
00:37:40,214 --> 00:37:42,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The landslide is smaller than before!</b></font>

332
00:37:46,114 --> 00:37:48,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You...you can't be serious!</b></font>

333
00:37:48,544 --> 00:37:51,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're not supposed to
overtake on this course!</b></font>

334
00:38:09,904 --> 00:38:12,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>W...what a guy...</b></font>

335
00:38:20,514 --> 00:38:27,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66" color="#ffff00"><b>{\an5}Ryosuke invited Takumi onto his new racing team,</b></font>

336
00:38:20,514 --> 00:38:27,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66" color="#ffff00"><b>{\an5}but Takumi couldn't reply immediately.</b></font>

337
00:38:20,514 --> 00:38:27,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66" color="#ffff00"><b>{\an5}So in order to test his newly reborn 86,</b></font>

338
00:38:20,514 --> 00:38:27,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66" color="#ffff00"><b>{\an5}Takumi heads to Kyoichi's home course for a battle.</b></font>

339
00:38:50,344 --> 00:38:52,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see. It's a little faster.</b></font>

340
00:38:53,534 --> 00:38:56,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Unlike a turbo, it's got the extended
acceleration of a mechanically tuned car.</b></font>

341
00:38:56,714 --> 00:39:00,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But no matter how you tune the car,
it's an Eight-Six after all.</b></font>

342
00:39:00,364 --> 00:39:02,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've got 350 HP.</b></font>

343
00:39:39,414 --> 00:39:42,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No matter what kind of car
I race against, I can't lose here.</b></font>

344
00:39:42,934 --> 00:39:47,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just like Ryosuke rules in Akagi,
I'm the emperor here.</b></font>

345
00:39:48,874 --> 00:39:50,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I won't miss my target
once I aim at it!</b></font>

346
00:39:55,204 --> 00:39:56,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's right on my tail.</b></font>

347
00:39:57,404 --> 00:39:59,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I just have to push myself
as much as possible.</b></font>

348
00:40:01,494 --> 00:40:06,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The slope will level out soon,
so the Eight-Six will lose speed.</b></font>

349
00:40:06,074 --> 00:40:09,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You won't be able to get away
from my counterattack.</b></font>

350
00:40:13,724 --> 00:40:14,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A bridge?</b></font>

351
00:40:14,684 --> 00:40:16,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The goal is near?!</b></font>

352
00:40:16,754 --> 00:40:19,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The steep slope is over.</b></font>

353
00:40:19,144 --> 00:40:21,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You'll need real power now.</b></font>

354
00:40:22,644 --> 00:40:26,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll show you the winning
formula of Sudo Kyoichi.</b></font>

355
00:40:30,844 --> 00:40:33,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>An optical illusion makes
the road look narrower...</b></font>

356
00:40:33,324 --> 00:40:35,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...and you can't approach
the outside enough.</b></font>

357
00:40:35,194 --> 00:40:38,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Once I poke my nose
out just a bit...</b></font>

358
00:40:43,234 --> 00:40:44,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The third bridge...!</b></font>

359
00:40:44,764 --> 00:40:47,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The inside and outside positions
will be reversed on the bridge.</b></font>

360
00:40:47,104 --> 00:40:49,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's my usual finish.</b></font>

361
00:40:49,654 --> 00:40:50,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see it.</b></font>

362
00:40:50,834 --> 00:40:51,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Go!</b></font>

363
00:40:53,324 --> 00:40:53,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No way!</b></font>

364
00:40:53,904 --> 00:40:55,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you want to die?!</b></font>

365
00:40:55,554 --> 00:40:56,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're going too fast!</b></font>

366
00:40:56,684 --> 00:40:57,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can't turn!</b></font>

367
00:40:57,754 --> 00:40:58,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It will turn.</b></font>

368
00:40:58,744 --> 00:41:01,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please turn, my Eight-Six!</b></font>

369
00:41:05,454 --> 00:41:06,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Can I?</b></font>

370
00:41:15,384 --> 00:41:21,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66" color="#ffff00"><b>{\an5}Kyoichi had been Kai Kogashiwa's target, so Kai</b></font>

371
00:41:15,384 --> 00:41:21,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66" color="#ffff00"><b>{\an5}decided to defeat Takumi instead.</b></font>

372
00:41:15,384 --> 00:41:21,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66" color="#ffff00"><b>{\an5}It turns out, Kai's father and Bunta used</b></font>

373
00:41:15,384 --> 00:41:21,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66" color="#ffff00"><b>{\an5}to be the fiercest of rivals.</b></font>

374
00:41:31,804 --> 00:41:32,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Five...</b></font>

375
00:41:32,884 --> 00:41:33,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...four...</b></font>

376
00:41:33,874 --> 00:41:34,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...three...</b></font>

377
00:41:34,894 --> 00:41:35,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...two...</b></font>

378
00:41:35,844 --> 00:41:36,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...one...</b></font>

379
00:41:36,844 --> 00:41:37,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Go!</b></font>

380
00:41:44,934 --> 00:41:45,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's fast.</b></font>

381
00:41:45,984 --> 00:41:48,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's not an ordinary Eight-Six.</b></font>

382
00:41:48,694 --> 00:41:52,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fine, that's what I want, too.</b></font>

383
00:41:52,284 --> 00:41:56,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll outrun your fast Eight-Six.</b></font>

384
00:42:13,414 --> 00:42:15,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There're so many
leaves tonight.</b></font>

385
00:42:15,844 --> 00:42:18,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And because of the wind, there are
piles of them here and there.</b></font>

386
00:42:18,704 --> 00:42:20,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If I go over them,
I'll instantly lose control.</b></font>

387
00:42:20,794 --> 00:42:22,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's so hard to drive.</b></font>

388
00:42:22,494 --> 00:42:25,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'd better let the car drift itself.</b></font>

389
00:42:26,234 --> 00:42:27,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're tough.</b></font>

390
00:42:27,644 --> 00:42:30,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A cheap trick won't work.</b></font>

391
00:42:30,044 --> 00:42:33,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The timing for trying that is important.</b></font>

392
00:42:34,134 --> 00:42:35,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have a bad feeling.</b></font>

393
00:42:35,714 --> 00:42:37,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's going to do something.</b></font>

394
00:42:45,274 --> 00:42:46,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Now!</b></font>

395
00:43:04,404 --> 00:43:06,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Once you let me get ahead,
you have no chance.</b></font>

396
00:43:08,984 --> 00:43:10,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've won this race!</b></font>

397
00:43:22,294 --> 00:43:24,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At this rate, the gap
will widen more.</b></font>

398
00:43:30,044 --> 00:43:30,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Go!</b></font>

399
00:43:46,734 --> 00:43:48,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What a guy!</b></font>

400
00:43:48,194 --> 00:43:50,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He managed to jump
on the first try!</b></font>

401
00:43:50,554 --> 00:43:53,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's got all the senses
of a mountain pass driver.</b></font>

402
00:44:17,694 --> 00:44:21,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can see the edge of asphalt
through the dried leaves.</b></font>

403
00:44:23,684 --> 00:44:25,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Now, that's the last chance!</b></font>

404
00:44:32,184 --> 00:44:33,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What the...?!</b></font>

405
00:44:33,164 --> 00:44:35,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>H...how did he accelerate like that?!</b></font>

406
00:44:38,344 --> 00:44:40,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What the hell happened?!</b></font>

407
00:44:40,474 --> 00:44:41,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Dammit all!</b></font>

408
00:44:45,684 --> 00:44:46,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here they come!</b></font>

409
00:44:46,344 --> 00:44:47,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who's ahead?!</b></font>

410
00:44:48,464 --> 00:44:49,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're side by side!</b></font>

411
00:44:50,054 --> 00:44:54,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Shit, if one misses the line,
both'll hit the concrete wall!</b></font>

412
00:45:30,404 --> 00:45:37,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66" color="#ffff00"><b>{\an5}With graduation in mind, Natsuki is eager to</b></font>

413
00:45:30,404 --> 00:45:37,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66" color="#ffff00"><b>{\an5}make up with Takumi.</b></font>

414
00:45:30,404 --> 00:45:37,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66" color="#ffff00"><b>{\an5}Around that time, her previous boyfriend Miki</b></font>

415
00:45:30,404 --> 00:45:37,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66" color="#ffff00"><b>{\an5}takes Natsuki on a drive in his car.</b></font>

416
00:45:30,404 --> 00:45:37,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66" color="#ffff00"><b>{\an5}Natsuki, seeking help, decides to call</b></font>

417
00:45:30,404 --> 00:45:37,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66" color="#ffff00"><b>{\an5}Takumi, who rushes to Mount Akina.</b></font>

418
00:45:49,904 --> 00:45:51,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hello...</b></font>

419
00:45:51,404 --> 00:45:53,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi, help me...lake...</b></font>

420
00:45:54,814 --> 00:45:55,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hello?</b></font>

421
00:45:55,914 --> 00:45:57,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is this Mogi?</b></font>

422
00:45:57,654 --> 00:45:58,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hello?</b></font>

423
00:46:02,344 --> 00:46:03,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Where are we going?</b></font>

424
00:46:03,404 --> 00:46:04,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Be prepared.</b></font>

425
00:46:04,454 --> 00:46:07,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I won't let you go
home until I'm satisfied.</b></font>

426
00:47:05,134 --> 00:47:06,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi!</b></font>

427
00:47:06,504 --> 00:47:07,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No way!</b></font>

428
00:47:19,564 --> 00:47:22,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi has come for me.</b></font>

429
00:47:28,674 --> 00:47:32,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wondered what his car is, but it's
a junker from the distant past.</b></font>

430
00:47:52,804 --> 00:47:57,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just three more curves, and
his car will be far behind.</b></font>

431
00:47:59,474 --> 00:48:00,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How could he?!</b></font>

432
00:48:08,034 --> 00:48:08,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Impossible!</b></font>

433
00:48:08,914 --> 00:48:11,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How could a junker like
that tailgate a 4WD?</b></font>

434
00:48:12,194 --> 00:48:13,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you look away,
you'll have an accident.</b></font>

435
00:48:17,554 --> 00:48:18,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How about this?</b></font>

436
00:48:20,554 --> 00:48:21,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not good...</b></font>

437
00:48:22,734 --> 00:48:23,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It won't turn!</b></font>

438
00:48:30,244 --> 00:48:32,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please, stay away!</b></font>

439
00:48:40,534 --> 00:48:41,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi!</b></font>

440
00:48:43,234 --> 00:48:49,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66" color="#ffff00"><b>{\an5}Takumi asks Ryosuke to battle him.</b></font>

441
00:48:43,234 --> 00:48:49,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66" color="#ffff00"><b>{\an5}By racing Ryosuke on his home course</b></font>

442
00:48:43,234 --> 00:48:49,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66" color="#ffff00"><b>{\an5}he hopes to find the answer</b></font>

443
00:48:43,234 --> 00:48:49,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66" color="#ffff00"><b>{\an5}to whether or not he should join the new team...</b></font>

444
00:49:03,374 --> 00:49:04,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A battle with me?</b></font>

445
00:49:05,944 --> 00:49:07,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah.
Please.</b></font>

446
00:49:08,524 --> 00:49:10,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I feel like I can find my answer.</b></font>

447
00:49:11,264 --> 00:49:12,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, let's begin.</b></font>

448
00:49:13,134 --> 00:49:14,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Go!</b></font>

449
00:49:25,174 --> 00:49:27,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can feel him so strongly.</b></font>

450
00:49:28,314 --> 00:49:33,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You must be concentrating on
driving as fast as you can.</b></font>

451
00:49:38,824 --> 00:49:41,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Show me your driving.</b></font>

452
00:49:47,954 --> 00:49:48,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Awesome.</b></font>

453
00:49:48,704 --> 00:49:50,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So exciting!
